[
  {
    "title": "",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "An Assassin is an agile hero that specializes in killing or disabling roaming targets picking them off as they try to replenish HP.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Assassin"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Focused on infiltration, deception, and mobility, Assassins are opportunistic hunters who find favorable moments within a fight before jumping into the fray.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Assassins"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "Regardless of the size of the enemy team, Assassins specialize in positioning and artful killing.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Assassins"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "They strike when the time is right – no sooner, no later."
          },
          {
            "text": "Assassins are more suitable to be played by experienced players as they have low HP and high burst damage.",
            "formatting": {
              "bold": [
                "Assassins"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "They are ideal for taking out opponents easily, but are easier to be killed due to bad positioning and wrong timing."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
